(Docker Guide \(Atho\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Last refresh: 2026-04-04.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This guide walks through building and running Atho nodes with Docker/Compose on Linux, macOS,) Tj
T*
(and Windows \(Docker Desktop\). It also shows how to run multiple nodes without port conflicts and) Tj
T*
(how to use the CLI container.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Prereqs) Tj
T*
(- Install Docker \(Docker Desktop on macOS/Windows; Docker Engine on Linux\).) Tj
T*
(- Optional: docker-compose v1/v2 \(Compose v2 is built into recent Docker Desktop\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What?s in the repo) Tj
T*
(- docker/Dockerfile: builds a Python 3.11 image, installs deps, builds falcon_cli, and runs) Tj
T*
(Src/Node/fullnode.py by default.) Tj
T*
(- docker/docker-entrypoint.sh: simple entrypoint wrapper.) Tj
T*
(- docker/docker-compose.yml: services fullnode, miner, miner2, optional fullnode2, and cli. P2P) Tj
T*
(is fixed to 56000 in-container; host ports are distinct \(56000/56001/56002/56003\). Miner APIs) Tj
T*
(use randomized host ports \(still 10200/10250 in-container\) to avoid conflicts.) Tj
T*
(- Bootstrap defaults: fullnode sets ATHO_BOOTSTRAP="" \(no external seed\); miners bootstrap to) Tj
T*
(fullnode:56000 on the compose network.) Tj
T*
(- P2P bootstrap seeds are now **env-only** \(ATHO_BOOTSTRAP as comma-separated host:port\); no) Tj
T*
(hardcoded seeds.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Quick start \(full node + miners + CLI, internal networking\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This builds the image and starts:) Tj
T*
(- fullnode: P2P 56000 and API 10100 inside the compose network.) Tj
T*
(- miner: P2P 56000 \(host bind 56001\) and API 10200 in-container \(host port randomized\);) Tj
T*
(bootstraps to fullnode:56000.) Tj
T*
(- miner2: P2P 56000 \(host bind 56003\) and API 10250 in-container \(host port randomized\);) Tj
T*
(bootstraps to fullnode:56000.) Tj
T*
(- cli: interactive CLI pointing at http://fullnode:10100.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Stop: docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml -f docker/docker-compose.override.yml down) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
