(- macOS/Windows: use Docker Desktop; commands are the same. Host volume paths may differ \(%cd%) Tj
T*
(or absolute paths\).) Tj
T*
(- ARM hosts: AVX2 is opt-in \(FALCON_USE_AVX2=true\). Keep the default \(false\) on ARM/older CPUs,) Tj
T*
(or provide a known-good prebuilt binary.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Troubleshooting) Tj
T*
(- Port in use: adjust host mappings in ports: or remove them to keep services internal.) Tj
T*
(- falcon_cli build fails: ensure build-essential/clang is present \(installed in Dockerfile\); if) Tj
T*
(AVX2 was enabled on an unsupported CPU, rebuild with FALCON_USE_AVX2=false.) Tj
T*
(- Map full errors: ensure the mounted volume has free space and raise the relevant LMDB size) Tj
T*
(ceiling if a store reaches its configured max; bounded AUTO_RESIZE_LMDB growth is already) Tj
T*
(supported and enabled in current code.) Tj
T*
(- CLI can?t connect: check NodePorts.json and ATHO_API_URL; ensure correct host/port mapping if) Tj
T*
(accessing from host.) Tj
T*
(- Miner not starting: ensure you?re running the miner service \(docker compose up miner\) and that) Tj
T*
(it can reach a bootstrap peer \(defaults to fullnode:56000 in compose\).) Tj
T*
(- Miner not starting: ensure you?re running the miner service \(docker compose -f) Tj
T*
(docker/docker-compose.yml -f docker/docker-compose.override.yml up miner\) and that it can reach) Tj
T*
(a bootstrap peer \(defaults to fullnode:56000 in compose\).) Tj
T*
(- Hashrate telemetry check: query /network/hashrate/live on your API port to verify local and) Tj
T*
(peer reports are being aggregated.) Tj
T*
